figdown 0.1 bitfield
title BGP message header — RFC 4271

# The 16-byte Marker spans four 32-bit rows automatically: a field
# wider than the unit continues onto the following rows (one field,
# not four — the .fd is the machine-readable truth).
bitfield bgp "BGP Message Header" unit=32 numbering=msb0
field Marker 128 note="all ones (RFC 4271 §4.1)"
field Length 16
field Type 8
